casebody.data:
WILSON LINE, INC., v. HERBERT C. BROWN. [No. 14,

April Term, 1933.]

Decided May 25th, 1933. The cause was argued before Bond, C. L, Pattison, Ukneb, Adkins, Oeeutt, Digges, Pabke, and Sloan, JL Wirt A. Duvall, Jr., with whom was Philip B. Perlman on the brief, for the appellant. Weinberg & Sweeten, submitting on brief, for the appellee. Bond, C. J.,

delivered the opinion of the Court.
